# Results

This directory is auto-generated when you run `python scripts/run_all.py`.

## Contents

| Directory | Contents |
|-----------|----------|
| `figures/` | All paper figures (ROC curves, SHAP plots, spectrograms, etc.) |
| `tables/`  | CSV files with numeric results (AUC, F1, precision, recall) |
| `models/`  | Model checkpoints (`.pt` files) |

Model checkpoints are excluded from version control via `.gitignore`.
CSV result tables are tracked so reviewers can verify numbers without re-running.
